🔹 Activate Virtual Environment (Windows)

venv\Scripts\activate






▶️ Start Backend (FastAPI)

uvicorn main:app --reload





💻 Start Frontend (if React)

cd D:\Projects\ShadowSCAN\ui
npm run dev





▶️ Generate Traffic

ping google.com -t

nmap -T5 -p- 127.0.0.1





🧪 Debug / Development Flow

# always first
git pull

# after work
git add .
git commit -m "your update"
git push